{"author":{"uri":{"label":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/reviews/id38618113"}, "name":{"label":"SceneCore_><"}, "label":""}, "updated":{"label":"2026-07-01T06:48:34-07:00"}, "im:rating":{"label":"2"}, "im:version":{"label":"7.129.0"}, "id":{"label":"14249564681"}, "title":{"label":"No hate, just my opinion.!"}, "content":{"label":"If you wanna put time into it, without spending money, this is NOT the right app. You can do very limited lessons a day for free. Also, I have been doing Italian for 3 years, and I still cannot speak properly. So I do NOT recommend those app.", "attributes":{"type":"text"}}, "link":{"attributes":{"rel":"related", "href":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/review?id=570060128&type=Purple%20Software"}}, "im:voteSum":{"label":"0"}, "im:contentType":{"attributes":{"term":"Application", "label":"Application"}}, "im:voteCount":{"label":"0"}}, 
{"author":{"uri":{"label":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/reviews/id1893303186"}, "name":{"label":"LunaSaidtoFixIt"}, "label":""}, "updated":{"label":"2026-07-01T06:42:55-07:00"}, "im:rating":{"label":"5"}, "im:version":{"label":"7.129.0"}, "id":{"label":"14249543721"}, "title":{"label":"I love it but.."}, "content":{"label":"I love this app, but we don’t want actual ads, go back to the Duolingo ads! Regular ads can have harmful viruses, so have actual ads is actually quite dangerous especially since you do have kids using this app and they can’t tell apart a legitimate ad from a sketchy one, so please go back to the original ads, yall make enough money to where this shouldn’t even happened. Now you got a bigger bug to fix. The actual unnecessary ads.", "attributes":{"type":"text"}}, "link":{"attributes":{"rel":"related", "href":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/review?id=570060128&type=Purple%20Software"}}, "im:voteSum":{"label":"0"}, "im:contentType":{"attributes":{"term":"Application", "label":"Application"}}, "im:voteCount":{"label":"0"}}, 
