{"author":{"uri":{"label":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/reviews/id1455442448"}, "name":{"label":"Strigaformes Pizzaria"}, "label":""}, "updated":{"label":"2026-07-01T06:19:24-07:00"}, "im:rating":{"label":"2"}, "im:version":{"label":"7.129.0"}, "id":{"label":"14249457535"}, "title":{"label":"It’s pretty great"}, "content":{"label":"Please add/fix\n1. A way to search the ‘words’ section by word or translation \n2. Something to spend gems on that’s actually worth it (maybe bring back the duo costumes, I dunno) \n3. Mini games later in the path, and more detailed, longer, and more interesting ones \n4. Way to select difficulty of ai in chess \n5. Revert the icons on the path to the old version with the little animated icons. Please. Please. They were so much better. \n6. The chests appear way too frequently, to the point where it’s rare to not have an xp boost. Every time I finish a lesson, I get like 4 chests projectile vomited at me. Also, they contain MORE. USELESS. GEMS.\n7. Something to buy with the gems. \n8. Please bring back the audio lessons; they were a great way to learn and had interesting stories \n\nUpdate: new unit tests absolutely SUCK, they are impossible and do not tell you the “correct” answer until it’s too late. Completely unclear how much you have to get right and what the heck you’re doing. Please revert back to the old system. It was much better there. \n\nOld review: \nThis is a great app and works great if you want to learn a language. \n\nPlease make the games more like games - they do not feel very challenging or engaging.\n\nLastly, certain exercises (no disternable pattern as to which) do not show up on the classroom dashboard. I sometimes have to do more than the required 3 in order for 3 to show up. Please fix, it’s super annoying.\n\nUpdate: just got to the end of lesson screen and there was none of the like, “you got this much % right” or “took this long”, nor a continue button. Then the app crashed. Still not sure if it logged as a completed exercise, even though on the path it shows as done.", "attributes":{"type":"text"}}, "link":{"attributes":{"rel":"related", "href":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/review?id=570060128&type=Purple%20Software"}}, "im:voteSum":{"label":"0"}, "im:contentType":{"attributes":{"term":"Application", "label":"Application"}}, "im:voteCount":{"label":"0"}}, 
