{"author":{"uri":{"label":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/reviews/id1919500697"}, "name":{"label":"MVP BRA WC"}, "label":""}, "updated":{"label":"2026-07-01T04:51:29-07:00"}, "im:rating":{"label":"5"}, "im:version":{"label":"7.129.0"}, "id":{"label":"14249153856"}, "title":{"label":"THE GOATED APP"}, "content":{"label":"A flash of green, a friendly chime,The daily push to make some time.A streak that grows day after day,To turn your learning into play.They call it the greatest, the ultimate app,A language guide right on your map.With bite-sized steps so clean and bright,It keeps the fire of habits alight.Küçük bir adım, her gün yeni bir kelime, (A small step, a new word every day,)Dil öğrenmek güzeldir, neşe verir kalbe. (Learning a language is beautiful, it brings joy to the heart.)Baykuş rehberlik eder çıktığın bu yolda, (The owl guides you on this path you've taken,)Başarı gizlidir sabırda ve her adımda. (Success is hidden in patience and in every step.)fun for all ages!!!", "attributes":{"type":"text"}}, "link":{"attributes":{"rel":"related", "href":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/review?id=570060128&type=Purple%20Software"}}, "im:voteSum":{"label":"0"}, "im:contentType":{"attributes":{"term":"Application", "label":"Application"}}, "im:voteCount":{"label":"0"}}, 
